<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-11-27T17:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-11-27T17:00:00-05:00" n="1008" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1008">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 838.105/38</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                Chargé <persName type="to">Mayer</persName>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-11-27T17:00:00-05:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">November 27, 1917, 5 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Your July 10, noon.<note n="4" xml:id="d1008fn4">Not printed.</note>
                            Amendment therein referred to has been consummated and put into effect
                            by an exchange of notes dated August 25 from Department to Haitian
                            Legation, answered by Haitian Legation in their note of August 29.
                            Department’s November 16, 3 p.m. instructs you to conclude second
                            modification.</p>
                        <p>Keep Department advised of progress.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>